All Implemented Interfaces:
com.kuka.common.events.IEventListener, ISessionEvents
public class CommandContainer<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISessionEvents

Container class for asynchronous message calls. This class is returned when calling an NCF method asynchronous und can be used to wait or get notifications upon an incoming response.
